{x_n} = \frac{a}{x_n}
x_{n+1} > \sqrt{a}
x_{n+1} = \frac{1}{2}\left(x_n + \frac{a}{x_n}\right) \ge \sqrt{x_n\frac{a}{x_n}} = \sqrt{a}
x_n > \sqrt{a} \implies \frac{a}{x_n} < \sqrt{a} < x_n
